OL,4,Casthma attack highlight dangers of
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FThe family of a 13-year-old girl who
OL,8,Fdied after an asthma attack led to a
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest have said they want to
OL,10,Fraise awareness of how serious the
OL,11,Fcondition can be, after feeling
OL,12,F"ignored" by doctors.
OL,14,FEmily Albino from Brent attended
OL,15,FNorthwick Park Hospital 10 times
OL,16,Fduring the last year of her life,
OL,17,Fsuffering with respiratory symptoms
OL,18,Fincluding coughing, shortness of
OL,19,Fbreath, headaches and fevers.
