OL,7,FShe was seen seven times in the Urgent
OL,8,FCare Centre and three times in the
OL,9,FPaediatric A&E department before she
OL,10,Fdied on December 16 2024.
OL,12,FHer parents said they were left
OL,13,Ffeeling 'constantly dismissed' when
OL,14,Fraising concerns over their daughter's
OL,15,Fworsening symptoms.
