OL,7,FEmily's mother Tatiana Albino
OL,8,Fdescribed how staff spoke to her when
OL,9,Fshe took her daughter to hospital,
OL,10,Ftelling ITV News London: "They don't
OL,11,Flisten to me. They think, like, I'm
OL,12,Fcrazy ... it's like I'm talking too
OL,13,Fmuch. I'm so desperate."
