OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FEmily's sister Nicole added: "Seeing
OL,8,Fhow bad it really was, it's just crazy
OL,9,Fbecause of how much my mum had to
OL,10,Ffight to get the best for Emily and
OL,11,Fshe never ended up getting it because
OL,12,Fof the amount of times that the
OL,13,Fhospital would completely just ignore
OL,14,Fher."
OL,16,FThe charity Asthma & Lung UK said for
OL,17,Fmost people asthma can be controlled
OL,18,Fwith medication but some cases sees
OL,19,Fthe condition becoming unstable and
OL,20,Fmore difficult to look after.
