OL,7,FMedical Director Nick Hopkinson told
OL,8,FITV News London: "Asthma is a serious,
OL,9,Flife-threatening condition for some
OL,10,Fpeople and not every asthma death can
OL,11,Fbe prevented.
OL,13,F"But it's certainly the case that many
OL,14,Fof those deaths could be prevented if
OL,15,Fthe health system was functioning
OL,16,Fproperly."
OL,18,FA year on from Emily's death her
OL,19,Ffamily now want to raise awareness
OL,20,Faround about the condition so other
OL,21,Ffamilies don't suffer unnecessarily.
