OL,7,FMrs Albino said: "My daughter is never
OL,8,Fcoming back to me ... but I need to
OL,9,Fsave lives ... I need to tell how
OL,10,Fserious asthma is."
OL,12,FThe London North West University
OL,13,FHealthcare NHS Trust said an
OL,14,Finvestigation into Emily's care found
OL,15,Fher treatment was "appropriate for her
OL,16,Fcondition" but there were several ways
OL,17,Fthe trust could have provided "better-
OL,18,Fcoordinated" care across different
OL,19,Fhealthcare teams.
