OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FA spokesperson told ITV News London:
OL,8,F"We apologise for the pain that this
OL,9,Fwill have caused Emily's family.
OL,11,F"As a result, we have made many
OL,12,Fimprovements to the way we manage
OL,13,Fasthma care for young people.
OL,15,F"This has included adding our asthma
OL,16,Faction plans to our electronic care
OL,17,Frecord so that they can be
OL,18,Fconsistently viewed by all our
OL,19,Fclinical teams and improving our
OL,20,Freferral processes to community teams
OL,21,Fand GPs including automated reminders.
